	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody1 width=50% ><a href="#Custom_Setting">[自定义位置]</a></td>
		<td class=tablebody1 width=50% ><a href="#Rule_Setting">[股市规则设置]</a></td>
	</tr>
	<form method="POST" action="?action=SaveSettimg">
	<tr>
		<th colspan="2" height="25" align="left" id="TableTitleLink"><a name=Gupiao_Setting></a>基本设置 [<a href="#top">顶部</a>] [<a href="#bottom">底部</a>]</th>
	</tr>	
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2 width="40%"><b>股票市场状态</b><br>股市是否开通</td> 
		<td class=tablebody1 width="60%">&nbsp;<input type=radio name="Gupiao_Setting(0)" value=1 <%if Gupiao_Setting(0)=1 then%>checked<%end if%>>打开&nbsp;<input type=radio name="Gupiao_Setting(0)" value=0 <%if Gupiao_Setting(0)=0 then%>checked<%end if%>>关闭&nbsp;</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2 width="40%"><b>关闭说明</b><br>在股市关闭的情况下显示，支持html语法</td> 
		<td class=tablebody1 width="60%">&nbsp;<textarea name="StopReadme" cols="40" rows="3"><%=StopGPReadme%></textarea>
		</td>
	</tr>	
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>自动刷新时间(秒)</b><br>股市首页自动刷新的时间间隔</td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="10" name="Gupiao_Setting(1)" value="<%=Gupiao_Setting(1)%>"> 秒
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>每页显示最多记录</b><br>用于股票所有和分页有关的项目</td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="10" name="Gupiao_Setting(2)" value="<%=Gupiao_Setting(2)%>"> 条
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>是否起用定时开关股市</b></td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=radio name="Gupiao_Setting(3)" value=1 <%if Gupiao_Setting(3)=1 then%>checked<%end if%>>是&nbsp;<input type=radio name="Gupiao_Setting(3)" value=0 <%if Gupiao_Setting(3)=0 then%>checked<%end if%>>否&nbsp;</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>股市开放时间</b><br>请确认您已经设置起用定时开关功能<br>起止小时用符号“||”分开</td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="10" name="Gupiao_Setting(4)" value="<%=Gupiao_Setting(4)%>"></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>股市名称</b></td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="35" name="Gupiao_Setting(5)" value="<%=Gupiao_Setting(5)%>"></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><a name=Gupiao_Setting1></a><b>防刷新机制</b><br>如选择打开请填写下面的限制刷新时间</td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=radio name="Gupiao_Setting(6)" value=1 <%if Gupiao_Setting(6)=1 then%>checked<%end if%>>打开&nbsp;<input type=radio name="Gupiao_Setting(6)" value=0 <%if Gupiao_Setting(6)=0 then%>checked<%end if%>>关闭&nbsp;</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>浏览刷新时间间隔</b><br>填写该项目请确认您打开了防刷新机制</td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="10" name="Gupiao_Setting(7)" value="<%=Gupiao_Setting(7)%>"> 秒</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>防刷新功能有效的页面</b><br>请确认您打开了防刷新功能<br>您指定的页面将有防刷新作用，用户在限定的时间内不能重复打开该页面，具有一定减少资源消耗的作用<br>每个页面名请用“|”符号隔开</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="35" name="Gupiao_Setting(8)" value="<%=Gupiao_Setting(8)%>"></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>删除不活动用户时间</b><br>可设置删除多少分钟内不活动用户<br>单位：分钟，请输入数字</td>
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="5" name="Gupiao_Setting(9)" value="<%=Gupiao_Setting(9)%>"> 分钟</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><a name=Gupiao_Setting2></a><b>随机事件发生概率</b><br>请输入(0～1)之间数值</td>
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="5" name="Gupiao_Setting(10)" value="<%=Gupiao_Setting(10)%>"></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>随机事件股价上涨的几率</b><br>发生随机事件时股价上涨的几率<br>股价下降的几率=1-股价上涨的几率</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="5" name="Gupiao_Setting(11)" value="<%=Gupiao_Setting(11)%>"></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>保留随机事件记录的条数</b><br>设置为0则保留所有随机事件记录</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="8" name="Gupiao_Setting(12)" value="<%=Gupiao_Setting(12)%>"> 条</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<th colspan="2" height="25" align="left" id="TableTitleLink"><a name=Trade_Setting></a>股票交易设置 [<a href="#top">顶部</a>] [<a href="#bottom">底部</a>]</th>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>是否允许交易</b><br>只有本项打开时股民才能进行股票买卖操作</td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=radio name="Trade_Setting(0)" value=1 <%if Trade_Setting(0)=1 then%>checked<%end if%>>是&nbsp;<input type=radio name="Trade_Setting(0)" value=0 <%if Trade_Setting(0)=0 then%>checked<%end if%>>否&nbsp;</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>成交量下限</b><br>当次买卖至少交易量<br>不做限制请设置为0</td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="10" name="Trade_Setting(2)" value="<%=Trade_Setting(2)%>"> 股</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>成交量上限</b><br>当次买卖至多交易量<br>不做限制请设置为0</td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="10" name="Trade_Setting(3)" value="<%=Trade_Setting(3)%>"> 股</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>交易次数限制</b><br>同一用户每天交易次数上限<br>不做限制请设置为0</td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="10" name="Trade_Setting(4)" value="<%=Trade_Setting(4)%>"> 次</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>手续费</b><br>每笔交易收取的手续费的百分数</td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="10" name="Trade_Setting(5)" value="<%=Trade_Setting(5)%>">  %</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>买入时差限制</b><br>同一用户买入同一种股票的时间间隔</td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="10" name="Trade_Setting(6)" value="<%=Trade_Setting(6)%>"> 分钟</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>卖出时差限制</b><br>同一用户卖出同一种股票的时间间隔</td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="10" name="Trade_Setting(7)" value="<%=Trade_Setting(7)%>"> 分钟</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>买卖时差限制</b><br>同一用户买入某股票后再卖出的时间间隔</td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="10" name="Trade_Setting(8)" value="<%=Trade_Setting(8)%>"> 小时</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>涨停上限</b><br>股票价格上涨率大于该值时出现涨停状态</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="10" name="Trade_Setting(9)" value="<%=Trade_Setting(9)%>"></td>
	</tr>	
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>跌停下限</b><br>股票价格下滑率大于该值时出现跌停状态</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="10" name="Trade_Setting(10)" value="<%=Trade_Setting(10)%>"></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>停牌条件</b><br>股票价格低于该值时出现停牌状态</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="10" name="Trade_Setting(11)" value="<%=Trade_Setting(11)%>"> 元</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>买入对股价的影响</b><br>购入股票时，股票价格 上涨、下降、不变的比例<br>上涨+下降<=1,不变的几率=1-上涨-下降</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="5" name="Trade_Setting(12)" value="<%=Trade_Setting(12)%>">：<input type=text size="5" name="Trade_Setting(13)" value="<%=Trade_Setting(13)%>">：<%=formatnumber(1-Trade_Setting(12)-Trade_Setting(13),2,true)%></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>卖出对股价的影响</b><br>抛出股票时，股票价格 下降、上涨、不变的比例<br>上涨+下降<=1,不变的几率=1-上涨-下降</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="5" name="Trade_Setting(14)" value="<%=Trade_Setting(14)%>">：<input type=text size="5" name="Trade_Setting(15)" value="<%=Trade_Setting(15)%>">：<%=formatnumber(1-Trade_Setting(14)-Trade_Setting(15),2,true)%></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<th colspan="2" height="25" align="left" id="TableTitleLink"><a name=PStock_Setting></a>个股上市设置 [<a href="#top">顶部</a>] [<a href="#bottom">底部</a>]</th>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>是否开启个股上市申请</b></td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=radio name="PStock_Setting(0)" value=1 <%if PStock_Setting(0)=1 then%>checked<%end if%>>是&nbsp;<input type=radio name="PStock_Setting(0)" value=0 <%if PStock_Setting(0)=0 then%>checked<%end if%>>否&nbsp;</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>最少具备资金</b><br>申请者现有的资金必须达到这个值才能申请个股上市</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="35" name="PStock_Setting(1)" value="<%=PStock_Setting(1)%>"> 元</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>最少上市数目</b><br>最少上市股票数目</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="35" name="PStock_Setting(5)" value="<%=PStock_Setting(5)%>"> 股</td>
	</tr>	
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>上市公司名称最小长度</b><br>填写数字，不能小于1大于50</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text name="PStock_Setting(2)" value="<%=PStock_Setting(2)%>"> byte</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>上市公司名称最大长度</b><br>填写数字，不能小于1大于50</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text name="PStock_Setting(3)" value="<%=PStock_Setting(3)%>"> byte</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>公司简介最大长度</b><br>填写数字，不能小于1大于255</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text name="PStock_Setting(4)" value="<%=PStock_Setting(4)%>"> byte</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<th colspan="2" height="25" align="left" id="TableTitleLink"><a name=AI_Setting></a>机器人(AI)设置 [<a href="#top">顶部</a>] [<a href="#bottom">底部</a>]</th>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>是否开启机器人</b><br>是否开启机器人事件，只有该项打开后下面的设置才生效</td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=radio name="AI_Setting(0)" value=1 <%if AI_Setting(0)=1 then%>checked<%end if%>>开启&nbsp;<input type=radio name="AI_Setting(0)" value=0 <%if AI_Setting(0)=0 then%>checked<%end if%>>关闭&nbsp;</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>AI操作几率</b><br>机器人发生买卖股票操作的概率<br>0～1之间的小数，值越大几率越大</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="8" name="AI_Setting(1)" value="<%=AI_Setting(1)%>"></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<th colspan="2" height="25" align="left" id="TableTitleLink"><a name=KaiHu_Setting></a>股市开户设置 [<a href="#top">顶部</a>] [<a href="#bottom">底部</a>]</th>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>是否允许开户</b></td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=radio name="KaiHu_Setting(0)" value=1 <%if KaiHu_Setting(0)=1 then%>checked<%end if%>>是&nbsp;<input type=radio name="KaiHu_Setting(0)" value=0 <%if KaiHu_Setting(0)=0 then%>checked<%end if%>>否&nbsp;</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>最少发帖数</b><br>限制必须达到这个数目才能在股市开户<br>不做限制请设置为0</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="8" name="KaiHu_Setting(1)" value="<%=KaiHu_Setting(1)%>"></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>最少魅力值</b><br>限制必须达到这个数目才能在股市开户<br>不做限制请设置为0</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="8" name="KaiHu_Setting(2)" value="<%=KaiHu_Setting(2)%>"></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>最少经验值</b><br>限制必须达到这个数目才能在股市开户<br>不做限制请设置为0</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="8" name="KaiHu_Setting(3)" value="<%=KaiHu_Setting(3)%>"></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>最少金钱值</b><br>限制必须达到这个数目才能在股市开户<br>不做限制请设置为0</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="8" name="KaiHu_Setting(4)" value="<%=KaiHu_Setting(4)%>"></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>原始资本</b><br>赠送给开户者的资本</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="10" name="KaiHu_Setting(6)" value="<%=KaiHu_Setting(6)%>"> 元</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<th colspan="2" height="25" align="left" id="TableTitleLink"><a name=User_Setting></a>股市帐户设置 [<a href="#top">顶部</a>] [<a href="#bottom">底部</a>]</th>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>是否允许从股票帐户提款</b></td> 
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=radio name="User_Setting(0)" value=1 <%if User_Setting(0)=1 then%>checked<%end if%>>是&nbsp;<input type=radio name="User_Setting(0)" value=0 <%if User_Setting(0)=0 then%>checked<%end if%>>否&nbsp;</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>是否允许存钱入股票帐户</b></td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=radio name="User_Setting(1)" value=1 <%if User_Setting(1)=1 then%>checked<%end if%>>是&nbsp;<input type=radio name="User_Setting(1)" value=0 <%if User_Setting(1)=0 then%>checked<%end if%>>否&nbsp;</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>取款上限</b><br>股民每次取款最大金额<br>不做限制请设置为0</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="8" name="User_Setting(2)" value="<%=User_Setting(2)%>"> 元</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=tablebody2><b>存款上限</b><br>股民每次存款最大金额<br>不做限制请设置为0</td>  
		<td class=tablebody1>&nbsp;<input type=text size="8" name="User_Setting(3)" value="<%=User_Setting(3)%>"> 元</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<th colspan="2" height="25" align="left" id="TableTitleLink"><a name=Custom_Setting></a>自定义位置设置 [<a href="#top">顶部</a>] [<a href="#bottom">底部</a>]</th>
